<item>
<title>[SSTMAEM2U-5] SST for FTT for MAE</title>
<link>https://jira.maybank.com.my/browse/SSTMAEM2U-5</link>
<project id="20509" key="SSTMAEM2U">MBB - SST on MAE and M2U</project>
<description><p>To introduce SST under the MAE screen as per below :</p> <div class='table-wrap'> <table class='confluenceTable'><tbody> <tr> <th class='confluenceTh'>FTT initiation</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Overseas Transfer type</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Tool tip</th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1406656/1406656_image-2025-07-30-16-10-37-380.png" height="247" width="101" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span>  </td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1508846/1508846_image-2025-10-03-09-25-53-619.png" height="332" width="118" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1406663/1406663_image-2025-07-30-16-11-43-498.png" height="362" width="167" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span>   <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1417509/1417509_image-2025-08-05-14-11-11-592.png" height="366" width="169" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer to login MAE using thier login credential and password<br/> 2) Customer to proceed with <br/> Transfer &gt; Overseas &gt; New / Fav transfer <br/> 3) The handling is as per BAU with no changes </td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer will then input the amount and select the currency to proceed<br/> 2) Titles with selection will be shown on the screen for customer selection<br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) To update the below to include <b>"(Includes 8% SST)" only if there is already a charges</b> - Service Fees  <ul class="alternate" type="square"> <li>Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees <br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>.</li> <li>Service Fees </li> <li>Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees <br/> c) The "Transfer" amount will add in the 8% SST also<br/> d) The total chages will be getting from DCC as per existing maintenance </li> <li><br/> <font color="#ff0000">Technical Changes<br/>  1. Create new feature flag for SST in DCC<br/> 2. Maintain SST amount and percentage in DCC<br/> 3. Add description for SST at the front end<br/> 4. Update tooltip content<br/> 5. Update Total Amount calculation to be inclusive of SST amount<br/> 6. To enhance button amount to inclusive service fee and SST</font></li> </ul> </td> <th class='confluenceTh'> &#124;&#124;<b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> To updated the tool tip for <br/>  <br/> a) "Agent/Beneficairy Bank Fee"<br/>  <br/> If you choose to pay this fee, the fee amount (inclusive of 8% SST) will be displayed on your confirmation page later. <br/> If you choose to let your recipient pay this fee, the fee amount will be deducted from the transfer amount.<br/>  <br/> b) Service Fees<br/>  <br/> The service fee (inclusive of 8% SST) will be paid from your local accounts during the transfer details later.&#124;&#124;</th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> </tr> </tbody></table> </div> <p> </p> <p> </p> <div class='table-wrap'> <table class='confluenceTable'><tbody> <tr> <th class='confluenceTh'>Transaction Flow</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Confirmation page </th> <th class='confluenceTh'>S2U screen</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Receipt page</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Statement/ M2U history/ M2U transaction history </th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1406669/1406669_image-2025-07-30-16-12-21-375.png" height="419" width="191" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'>  <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1511613/1511613_image-2025-10-06-11-17-08-380.png" height="863" width="189" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/> <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1508852/1508852_image-2025-10-03-09-26-40-192.png" height="435" width="145" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/>  </td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1417521/1417521_image-2025-08-05-14-13-25-460.png" height="272" width="118" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1406695/1406695_image-2025-07-30-16-15-40-395.png" height="346" width="142" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1406702/1406702_image-2025-07-30-16-15-55-054.png" height="387" width="142" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/>  <br/> Transaction History is based on the file <br/> <span class="nobr"><a href="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1546584/1546584_Transaction+History_SST+Updated.xlsx" title="Transaction History_SST Updated.xlsx attached to SSTMAEM2U-5">Transaction History_SST Updated.xlsx<sup><img class="rendericon" src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif" height="7" width="7" align="absmiddle" alt="" border="0"/></sup></a></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1508853/1508853_image-2025-10-03-09-26-55-143.png" height="329" width="99" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'><font color="#ff0000"> </font></td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer to input all the field as per BAU today with no changes </td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) All the information poulated is as per customer's input<br/> 2) The handling of all the CTA will not have any changes and it is as per BAU<br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) To introduce the field in the screens:- <br/> <font color="#de350b">i) Principal </font><br/> <font color="#de350b">ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">iii) Service Fee</font><font color="#de350b">iv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)</font><font color="#de350b">v) Agent Fee</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</font><br/>  <br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>. - Service Fees  - Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/>  <br/> <font color="#ff0000">Technical Changes</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000"> 1. Update ChargesInquiry API to add 3 new field</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">- SST Type</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">- Debiting Account</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">- GCIF</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">2. To use SST amount for Service Fee and Agent Fee from inquiry response </font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">3. Add description for SST at the front end</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">4. To show new lines for Agent Fee SST and Service Fee SST</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">5. Update Total Amount calculation to be inclusive of SST amount</font></td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) The handling will be as per BAU but reflecting the new amount which includes SST<br/>  <br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) <font color="#de350b">To reflect the total amount the screen </font><b><font color="#de350b">(Includes 8% SST)"</font> if there is charges applies</b> - Service Fees<br/> -Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees <br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>.<br/> -Service Fees <br/> -Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/> c) The "Transfer" amount will add in the 8% SST <br/> d) The total chages will be getting from DCC as per existing maintenance &#124;For each transaction with<br/> e) To remove the field of service charges and agent/ bene fees in S2U as it is repeated as per the total amount bracket<br/>  <br/> <font color="#de350b">Technical Changes<br/> 1. To implement v5 s2u - TESTING WILL REMAIN USING BAU FOR THE CURRENT VERSION</font><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">2. To remove existing field service fee and agent fee field -</font></del> <font color="#de350b">TO BE IMPLEMENTED IN V5</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">3. To include SSt amount in the transfer amount</font><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">4. To add SST description content</font></del><br/>  <br/>  </td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer then proceed with S2U and click PDF to generate receipt page<br/> 2) All the information will be as per customer's input<br/>  <br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) To introduce the field in the screen <b>(Includes 8% SST)" if there is charges applies</b> <br/> <font color="#de350b"><del>i) Principal</del> </font><br/> <font color="#de350b">ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)</font><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">iii) Service Fee</font><font color="#de350b">iv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)</font><font color="#de350b">v) Agent Fee</font></del><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</font></del><br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>.<br/> -Service Fees <br/> -Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/> c) The "Transfer" amount will add in the 8% SST <br/> d) The total chages will be getting from DCC as per existing maintenance &#124;For each transaction with</td> <td class='confluenceTd'><font color="#ff0000">Technical Changes</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">1. To show new lines for Agent Fee SST and Service Fee SST</font><br/> <font color="#ff0000">2. Update Total Amount calculation to be inclusive of SST amount</font><br/>  <br/>  &#124;<b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) Principal<br/> b) Service Fees<br/> c) Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/>  <br/> <font color="#172b4d">There will be 5 lines created which follow  </font><br/> <font color="#172b4d">i) Principal </font><br/> <font color="#172b4d">ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)</font><br/> <font color="#172b4d">iii) Service Feeiv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)v) Agent Fee</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</font><br/> <font color="#172b4d">**When user click the receipt from the same transaction it will show the same receipt (e.g. if user click receipt in service tax agent fee lines it will show the receipt for the whole transaction)</font><br/> Technical Changes1. To show new lines for Agent Fee SST, Agent Fee SST, Service Fee, Service Fee SST and Principal</td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'><font color="#ff0000"> </font></td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'><font color="#ff0000"> </font></td> </tr> </tbody></table> </div> <p> <br/>  <br/>  <br/>  </p> <p> </p></description>
